    "transliteration": "Method: It is 2 rak'at Namaz (Like morning prayers). To be prayed at the time of travel.\r\n\r\nAfter this Namaz recite the following Dua:\r\n\r\nBISMILLAHIR RAHMANIR RAHEEM ALLAAHUMMA INNEE ASTAWDE-O'KAS SAA-A'TA NAFSEE WA AHLEE WA MAALEE WA WALADEE WA ZURRIYYATEE WA DUNYAAYA WA AAKHERATEE WA KHAATAMATE A'MALEE ALLAAHUMMAH FIZ A'LAYNAA ALLAAHUMMAJ A'LNAA FEE JAWAAREKA ALLAAHUMMA LAA TASLUBNAA NE'MATEKA WA LAA TO-GHAYYERO MAA BENAA MIN A'AFEYATEKA WA FAZLEKA YAA MAWLAAYAN QATA-A'R RAJAA-O ILLAA MINKA WA KHAABATIL AMALUL AAFEEKA AS-ALOKA ELAAHEE MAN HAQQAHU WAAJEBUN A'LAYKA MIMMAN JA-A'LTA LAHUL HAQ I'NDAKA AN TOSALLEYA A'LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN AN TAQZEYA HAAJATEE.\r\n\r\nThen say:\r\n\r\nMOHAMMADUN RASOOLUL LAAHE AMAAMEE WA A'LIYYUN WARAA-EE WA FAATEMATO FAWQA RAASEE WAL HASANO WAL HOSAYNO A'LAA YASAAREE, WA A'LIYYUN WA MOHAMMADUN WA JA'FARUN WA MOOSAA WA A'LIYYUN WA MOHAMMADUN WA A'LIYYUN WAL HASANO WAL HUJJATO A'LAYHEMUS SALAAMO HAWLEE ELAAHEE MAA KHALAQTA KHALQAN KHAYRAM MINHUM FAJ-A'L SALAWAATEE BEHIM MAQBOOLATAN WA DA'WAATEE BEHIM MUSTAJAABATAN WA HAWAA-EJEE BEHIM MAQZIYYATAN WA ZONOOBEE BEHIM MAGHFOORATAN WA AAFAATEE BEHIM MADFOO-A'TAN WA A-A'DAA-EE BEHIM MAQHOORATAN WA RIZQEE BEHIM MABSOOTATAN ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A'LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMAD.\r\n\r\n(Misbah Part 23, Pg. 186-187)", 
